{"tid":815704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國外交部亦向香港的國民發出旅遊提示","createTime":"2018-09-12T08:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T09:36:46.000Z","uid":78873,"like":402,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac5342f203a2493e4c4afd83fca0c4149fddd57","tid":815704,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180912/58672482\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F58672482&d=LQWnglECIL2He5N2i7ZqgF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=eff5f525\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F58672482&h=b7afe9cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180912/58672482</a><br />\n<br />\n天文台高級科學主任林靜芝中午見記者時警告，山竹環流很廣闊，且風力強勁，進入南海後，會迅速撲向廣東沿岸，威脅相當大。山竹的路徑雖仍有變數，但預期周日會為本港帶來惡劣天氣。英國外交部亦向<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港的國民</span>發出旅遊提示，指山竹可能在周日，為香港的海面及天氣帶來危險狀況，呼籲國民周日若在香港，要留意風暴消息，並聽從當地政府建議。<br />\n<br />\n大英袓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f126487f4a2ec72d4df6c40ef8ac54fae835d8f4","tid":815704,"uid":6964,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:42:45.000Z","msg":"🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧"},{"pid":"065b075fee2c7f768cd92a53bf3f097a4cbe4828","tid":815704,"uid":78873,"like":147,"dislike":4,"score":143,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/164944_b64810fde7027715e614449aff1d595f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F164944_b64810fde7027715e614449aff1d595f.png&h=cad4a40a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice/hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fforeign-travel-advice%2Fhong-kong&d=LQWnglECIL2He5N2i7ZqgF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9922c980\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice/hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\nTyphoon Mangkhut is forecast to bring hazardous sea and weather conditions to Hong Kong from around Sunday 16 September; you should monitor the progress of approaching storms and follow the advice of local authorities<br />\n<br />\nThe typhoon season in Hong Kong normally runs from April to October. Typhoon Mangkhut is forecast to bring hazardous sea and weather conditions to Hong Kong from around Sunday 16 September. You should monitor the progress of approaching storms and follow the advice of the local authorities. See Natural disasters<br />\n<br />\n各位國民請注意大英袓國予各位之提示，颱風情況下敬請注意安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be927cd89e233a8127229c1d1bed83e1cb528c33","tid":815704,"uid":25858,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:55:56.000Z","msg":"國民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6bf5b1364761d1c67dc7e9b964bb4520648b03","tid":815704,"uid":78873,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"quote":{"pid":"be927cd89e233a8127229c1d1bed83e1cb528c33","tid":815704,"uid":25858,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:55:56.000Z","msg":"國民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"國民 即 Nationals<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不單指 BC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419e23689e5b60410da2d66761cdbe2fa4f861f0","tid":815704,"uid":20924,"like":60,"dislike":64,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:48:04.000Z","msg":"過份解讀<img src=\"/asset